<Characteristic xsi:noNamespaceSchemaLocation="http://schemas.bluetooth.org/Documents/characteristic.xsd" name="Chromaticity Coordinate" type="org.bluetooth.characteristic.chromaticity_coordinate" uuid="2B1C" last-modified="2017-07-11" approved="Yes" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance">
  <InformativeText>
    <Abstract>This characteristic represents a chromaticity coordinate in a color diagram such as the CIE1931 diagram. It can represent an x or y coordinate.</Abstract>
